                    Tableau Dashboards
                </h1>

                <!-- Subtitle -->
                <p class="font-semibold leading-8 text-center py-4">
                    Some of my data dashboard on Tableau Public.
                </p>
            </a>

            <!-- Text & Image -->
            <div class="text-pretty leading-8 flex items-start space-x-8">
                <!-- Text -->
                <div class="flex-1 box-border">
                    <p class="text-pretty">
                        Tableau is a Business Intelligence software but with a
                        nicer look than Power BI for example. Check out my public dashboards <a
                            href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/marco.zausch8856/vizzes"
